content: Love it!
Great app. Had a few issues setting notification sounds but developer customer service was superb and resolved it promptly.
replyContent:
Please check 2 things.

1. After tapping COMMUNICATOR: 01, tap NOTIFICATION.
Then press menu-> [MAIN DIRECTORY] -> [NOTIFICATIONS] -> (complete action with "Media Storage") and check that COMMUNICATOR: 01 is selected.

2. Check that you didn't set computer 01 as the custom notification sound for the contact you received an alert from.
